title: Friday's Prep Football Roundup
text:
Friday's Prep Football Roundup Mount Tabor 55, Reynolds 21 
It was a night of big plays Friday for the Mount Tabor in a 55-21 win over Reynolds in a Central Piedmont 4-A game.
